952
00:58:00,859 --> 00:58:01,960
Sadarlah.

953
00:58:25,889 --> 00:58:26,960
Seorang kaki tangan?

954
00:58:27,020 --> 00:58:29,290
Kamu tidak ingin tahu siapa dia? Ingin kuberi tahu?

955
00:58:31,129 --> 00:58:32,730
Biar kuberi tahu.

956
00:58:35,230 --> 00:58:36,470
Ibumu, Do Hyun Sook.

